  "notes": "Native `tput`/`clear` binaries (crates/ncurses-tools) emit byte-identically to the system tools across string caps (tparm+tputs: cup/setaf/setab/bold/...), number caps (cols/lines), `longname`, and `clear`. `tput clear`/`clear` append the `E3` clear-scrollback extension, exercising the new extended (user-defined) terminfo reader. Closes part of BLD-03 (CLI tools as native binaries).",
